'From Squeak4.4 of 31 December 2012 [latest update: #12327] on 24 August 2013 at 10:59:21 pm'!"Change Set:		LanguageEnvironmentFromLocaleIdWithFallback-MUDate:			24 August 2013Author:			Masashi UmezawaFixed LanguageEnvironment>>localeID: to use lang only locale id as fallback.For example, if there is no 'ja-JP' locale, it uses 'ja' locale as a fallback."!!LanguageEnvironment class methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'mu 8/18/2013 23:20'!localeID: localeID	^self knownEnvironments at: localeID ifAbsent: [ | fallbackLocId |		fallbackLocId := LocaleID isoLanguage: localeID isoLanguage.		 self knownEnvironments at: fallbackLocId ifAbsent: [ 			self localeID: (LocaleID isoLanguage: 'en')]]! !